In the context of RosettaJS, the &#64;Command is a Notes Formula function that
does not exist in the functions of the Notes Formula language but rather an
&#64;Command command itself that accepts the command name to execute as its first
argument and the accompanying command parameters as arguments 2 through n.

@param {string} commandName The name of the command you want to perform. See {@link https://help.hcltechsw.com/dom_designer/14.0.0/basic/H_COMMANDS_LISTED.html|www.hcltechsw.com }
