@see For further information, see &nbsp;{@link https://help.hcltechsw.com/dom_designer/14.0.0/basic/H_EXP.html | www.hcltechsw.com}&nbsp;and&nbsp;{@link https://docs.oasis-open.org/office/OpenDocument/v1.3/cs02/part4-formula/OpenDocument-v1.3-cs02-part4-formula.html#EXP | docs.oasis-open.org}
@example rosetta.exp(1); // returns 2.718281828459045
