@see For further information, see &nbsp;{@link https://docs.oasis-open.org/office/OpenDocument/v1.3/cs02/part4-formula/OpenDocument-v1.3-cs02-part4-formula.html#FACT       | docs.oasis-open.org}
@example rosetta.fact(6) // returns 720

factDouble.!doc:
