@param {*} value any value
@returns {boolean} True if the value ia a time-date or a time-date list. Othewise false.
@see For further information, see &nbsp;{@link https://help.hcltechsw.com/dom_designer/14.0.0/basic/H_ISTIME.html|www.hcltechsw.com}
@example
