lower.!doc:
Converts text to lowercase.

@param {string} text The text you want to convert to lowercase. LOWER does not change characters in text that are not letters.
@returns {string} The lower case text.
@see For further information, see &nbsp;{@link https://docs.oasis-open.org/office/OpenDocument/v1.3/cs02/part4-formula/OpenDocument-v1.3-cs02-part4-formula.html#LOWER | docs.oasis-open.org}
@example
