@returns {number} The truncated for of the number with the given precision.
@see For further information, see &nbsp;{@link https://docs.oasis-open.org/office/OpenDocument/v1.3/cs02/part4-formula/OpenDocument-v1.3-cs02-part4-formula.html#TRUNC | docs.oasis-open.org}
